  "Description": {
    "English": "This pupa, pulsating and warm, has begun its transformation from throbbing sac of mucus into an unspeakably vile insectoid.<br><br>Theoretically processable in a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Nutrient Processor</span> to generate edible products.<br><br><span class=\"name name-fuel\">WARNING</span>: grub-sac will release powerful pheromones if violated.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "散发着温度的蛹正在不停颤动，它即将从外壳里不断跳动的黏液变为难以言喻的邪恶昆虫。<br><br>理论上来说能够在<span class=\"name name-technology\">营养处理器</span>中加工为可食用的产品。<br><br><span class=\"name name-fuel\">警告</span>：如果被破坏，虫蛹将释放出一种极其强大的信息素。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "這些規律搏動、溫熱的蟲蛹，準備從顫動的液囊變成不可言狀的邪惡昆蟲機器人。<br><br>理論上可以使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">營養處理器</span>加工生產為食品。<br><br><span class=\"name name-fuel\">警告</span>：若幼蟲囊遭到侵擾，就會釋放強力費洛蒙。"
  },
